public class SinglyLinkedOrderedList<T> extends SinglyLinkedList<T> implements OrderedListADT<T>
This class is an implementation of the Ordered List, which used a singly linked list as support. It implements the OrderedListADT, and extends SinglyLinkedList abstract class
